channel.title: Can someone make me a server etc?
channel.description:
Hi, I have been downloading servers like blakescape, testcape, demonscape, etc. i tried eiditing it all myself and then it all fails and goes haywire, so i was wandering if someone could make me one, i will tell you everything i want on it, or you could set up the basic stuff for me and give me the files to add on what i want, and if you make a character on it, i will make you an admin with everything you want on there, i would like it to be called mikescape and be able to work with freewebs if put it on there.
If anyone is interested, either email me on [email]drgn24b@tiscali.co.uk[/email], reply to this post, or go onto this website [url=http://mikescape.myfastforum.org/]http://mikescape.myfastforum.org/[/url].
Thank you :D
